comments.body: I have been traveling for work, so I have not been able to check on this throughout yesterday. I bid on four coins. With the posted pictures I assumed the stickers and PK were included. In fact, they were why I was excited to buy multiple of these. I see Cas 5s for sale a lot but not the whole package. Anyway, I would like to retract my bid for four coins and decrease it to 2. I trust the forum to let me know if this is out of line, but I feel this is ok on my part due to the confusion of what was actually being sold. Steeley
